作者 | 罗松松  编辑 | 张庆宁    出品|棱镜·腾讯小满工作室欢迎下载腾讯新闻APP，阅读更多优质资讯尹雄平是壹米滴答公司驻武汉的一名货车司机，也是一名退伍军人。
Welcome to download Tencent News APP. Read more about quality information. Yin is a truck driver and a veteran at One-meter Tricktock in Wuhan.
1月25日一早，他和公司另一位司机黄明军从武汉分拨中心驱车赶往100多公里远的湖北仙桃。
Early January 25, he and another company driver, Huang Mingjun, drove more than 100 kilometers from the Wuhan allocation center to Hubei Xiantao.
两人等了12个小时，从当地一家工厂里拉到100万个口罩和200件防护服，次日凌晨四点送抵武汉。
The two men waited 12 hours, pulled a million masks and 200 protective clothing from a local factory and arrived in Wuhan at 4 a.m. the next morning.
1月26日上午，当尹雄平在休息时，壹米滴答湖北公司将这些这批医疗防护用品送到武汉协和医院、湖北省第三人民医院、武汉市中医医院、武汉市第三医院。
On the morning of January 26, when Yin Xiongping was at rest, one metre of Hubei company delivered these medical protection articles to Wuhan Concorde Hospital, Hubei Third People's Hospital, Wuhan TCM Hospital and Wuhan Third Hospital.
每家医院获得20万个救急口罩。
Each hospital was provided with 200,000 emergency masks.
为这批医疗防护用品买单的是宁波当地企业，壹米滴答是运货方。
Pay for this group of medical protection supplies is Ningbo local enterprises, one meter tick is the freight side.
来自四面八方的医疗防护用品正源源不断涌向武汉及周边城市，武汉市物流协会紧急协调货车、司机。
Medical protection supplies from all sides are pouring into Wuhan and surrounding cities, Wuhan Logistics Association emergency coordination of trucks and drivers.
壹米滴答公司为武汉各医院运送医疗物资货车司机拉来四百箱口罩25日早上8点多，壹米滴答的货车司机尹雄平和黄明军从武汉分拨中心出发。
One meter ticker company for Wuhan hospitals to transport medical supplies truck drivers to pull 400 boxes of masks more than 8 a.m. on the 25th, one meter tick truck driver Yin Xiongping and Huang Mingjun from the Wuhan sub-center.
路上他们碰到交警，因这次任务公司报备着急，没有拿到特别通行证。
On the way they met the traffic police, because this task company reported anxious, did not get a special pass.
两人把报备审批记录拿给交警，交警没有多问就放行了，最后不忘嘱咐一句：“你们必须两个人去，两个人回。
The two men presented the examination and approval record to the traffic police, who released the report without asking any more questions.
中午11点多，尹雄平到达仙桃市彭场镇一家工厂。
At 11: 00 noon, Yin Xiongping arrived at a factory in Pengchang Town, Xiantao City.
壹米嘀答的领导跟他俩说，等到晚上7点多才能拉到货，建议他们开一间房休息一下。
The one-meter-long leader told them that they could not get the goods until after 7pm, and suggested that they open a room for a rest.
尹雄平知道自己是从武汉过去，“尽量别开了，别难为酒店的人。
Yin Xiongping knew that he was from Wuhan, "try not to open, do not be difficult for the hotel people.
”领导只好作罢，“你们委屈一下，在车上面先休息。
"The leader had to stop." You all have a grievance and rest on top of the car.
”两人随时待命，哪儿都不敢去。
They stood by at any moment, afraid to go anywhere.
下午两点多，尹雄平实在太饿了，刚好遇到优速快递的同事，想委托他们带一批口罩回武汉，就问他能不能绕个路，“去附近超市给我们带一点吃的。
More than 2: 00 pm, Yin Xiongping is really too hungry, just met with your express colleagues, want to entrust them with a batch of masks back to Wuhan, asked him if he can detour, "to the nearby supermarket to bring us some food.
”下午4点多，两人吃到一点东西。
It was after four o'clock in the afternoon, and they had something to eat.
口罩的需求量实在是太大了，这家仙桃工厂一直在赶工，还是凑不齐他俩的货。
The demand for masks was so great that the nectarine factory kept on working and couldn't get their stuff together.
两人从下午6点多又等到晚上9点多，之后又等了两个多小时，晚上11点多才开始装货，一直装到凌晨2点多。
They waited from 6 p.m. until after 9 p.m., and then waited for more than two hours before loading began at more than 11 p.m. and continued to load until after 2 a.m.
清点货品完毕，尹雄平和同事拉着整整400多箱口罩回到武汉，彼时已经是凌晨四点，之后再由其他同事派送给了上述医院。
After the goods were counted, Yin Xiongping and his colleagues returned to Wuhan with more than 400 cases of masks. It was then four in the morning and sent to the hospital by other colleagues.
“有人事情就好办”罗宽是尹雄平的领导，壹米滴答湖北省区办公室主任，这段时间他的工作主要是两件事。
"Some things are easy to do" Luo Hung-ping is the leader of Yin Xiongping, one meter Ditto Hubei District Office Director, during this time his work is mainly two things.
第一是内部防控。
The first is internal control.
公司决定成立管理小组，针对湖北省的1200多名员工进行身体状况的摸排调查，尤其是排查其中一部分春节期间滞留武汉的员工。
The company decided to set up a management team to survey more than 1,200 employees in Hubei province, especially those who stayed in Wuhan during the Spring Festival.
对于有感染风险的员工，进行及时了解和跟进，除此之外对分拨中心按时消毒。
For staff at risk of infection, timely understanding and follow-up, in addition to the distribution center on time disinfection.
第二是物资运输。
The second is the transportation of materials.
罗宽等管理层发动该公司的武汉司机和管理人员参与到疫情防治和物资运输当中。
Luo Kuan and other management launched the company's Wuhan drivers and managers to participate in the prevention and control of the epidemic and transport of materials.
罗宽的电脑从早上一直开到晚上十一二点，微信群里不断有各种信息，太多事情需要他及时沟通。
Lo Kuan's computer was open from morning till 11: 12 pm, and there was so much information in the microphone group that he needed to communicate in time.
壹米滴答在武汉共有20多号员工、30多辆货车，处于随时待命的战备状态。
One meter ticking in Wuhan has more than 20 employees, more than 30 trucks, on standby at all times.
“我们给他们准备了口罩，对车辆进行消毒，保障他们安全。
"We provided them with masks, disinfected the vehicles and made them safe.
”罗宽说。
'he said.
1月26日上午，罗宽接到任务，火神山正在建立“小汤山”医院，正在赶工建设，需要建筑建材，“武汉市物流协会安排我们承接了一部分水电和线缆设备的运输工作。
On the morning of January 26, Luo Kuan received a mission to set up the "Xiaotangshan" Hospital, construction work is under way, need building materials, "Wuhan City Logistics Association arranged for us to take over a part of the transportation of hydropower and cable equipment.
”现在来看，全国支援武汉的医疗物资比较充足，社会零散资源正在逐步集结。
"Wuhan is now supported by adequate medical supplies, social resources are gradually concentrated.
“物资运抵武汉之后，再及时运到县城和乡镇，需要更多的货车司机。
"Materials arrived in Wuhan, and then in time to the county and township, need more truck drivers.
”罗宽说，“有人事情就好办。
'said Lo Kwan.' Things are easy for somebody.
”罗宽说，现在正好是春节，很多货车司机都在外地过年。
'It's Spring Festival and many truck drivers are away for the New Year, 'Mr. Luo said.
武汉物流协会紧急调配怎么办？1月23号武汉封城开始，武汉市物流协会陆续收到了一些公司的求助。
Wuhan Logistics Association emergency deployment? January 23, Wuhan began to seal the city, Wuhan City Logistics Association has received a number of companies for help.
“春节期间，他们很多司机都放假了，大批货物想运往武汉，但没人，希望我们可以帮忙。
"During the Spring Festival, many of their drivers have holidays, and a lot of goods want to be shipped to Wuhan, but no one, I hope we can help.
”协会秘书长石君说。
"said Shi Jun, the association's general secretary.
武汉市物流协会随即建立两个微信群，一个是大车组，一个是小车组，大车主要负责运送大型医疗物资，小车（主要是私家车）负责接送医护人员下班，运输小件医疗物资和生活物资到医院和社区。
Wuhan Municipal Logistics Association immediately set up two micro-groups, one is a large car group, a large car mainly responsible for transporting large medical supplies, small cars (mainly private cars) to transport medical personnel off duty, small medical supplies and supplies to hospitals and communities.
石君等人负责收集和梳理信息，并且进行车辆、司机进行调度。
Shijun and others are responsible for collecting and combing information and dispatching vehicles and drivers.
有些外地物资如果进不了武汉市内，武汉市物流协会安排车辆在周边的高速路口进行交接，条件允许的，现场直接分拨派送，分拨不了的暂时拉到仓库之后再进行周转。
If some foreign materials can not enter Wuhan, Wuhan Municipal Logistics Association arranged for vehicles at the surrounding high-speed intersection to carry out handover, conditions permitting, directly on-site distribution, the allocation of temporary to the warehouse and then turn over.
“我们主要负责点对点的运输，将医疗防护用品直接运到医院和社区，将建材运到正在赶工建设的火神山医院工地上。
"We are primarily responsible for point-to-point transportation, delivering medical supplies directly to hospitals and communities, and transporting building materials to the building site of Mount Fujimori Hospital, where construction is proceeding apace.
”石君说。
"said Shi Jun.
截至1月27日中午，武汉市物流协会集结的志愿货车车队合计承运口罩120余万只、防护服200余箱、保障食品饮料2000余箱、水暖建材100多立方，一定程度上缓解了武汉市防疫保障物资供需矛盾。
By noon on January 27, the Wuhan Municipal Logistics Association had assembled a convoy of voluntary goods vehicles carrying more than 1.2 million face masks, over 200 boxes of protective clothing, over 2,000 boxes of food and beverages, and over 100 cubic meters of building materials for water and heating, alleviating to a certain extent the contradiction between the supply and demand for epidemic prevention supplies in Wuhan.
各路医疗支援物资还在源源不断进入武汉，但武汉市内以及武汉和周边城市之间的中短途运输存在缺口。
Medical support materials continue to flow into Wuhan, but Wuhan city and Wuhan and surrounding cities between the short and medium transport gap.
在武汉工作的货车司机多为外地人，其中一些愿意返回武汉驰援。
The truckers working in Wuhan are mostly foreigners, some of whom are willing to return to Wuhan to help.
“有些人可能需要暂时在一家隔离一段时间，这是防范疫情需要。
"Some people may need to be temporarily isolated for a period of time, which is necessary to prevent an outbreak.
如果开着货车回到武汉，市内运输需接受一定管制。
If driving a lorry back to Wuhan, the city's transportation needs to be subject to certain control.
”石君说。
"said Shi Jun.
武汉市物流协会已经跟武汉交通部门反映过这些问题，“交通部门给了我们表格样式，让我们填入司机和车辆信息，好将他们统一调配回来。
Wuhan Municipal Logistics Association and Wuhan Transport Department have reflected these problems, "the traffic department has given us a form model, let us fill in the driver and vehicle information, so they can be unified back.
”石君认为，这是比较可行的解决方案。
Mr Shi believes this is a more feasible solution.
